Use science-based standards with transparent metrics, pair enforcement for major polluters with tools like tax credits, competitive grants, and performance-based compliance options, and phase in changes to avoid shocks. Invest in modern infrastructure and targeted transition support—retraining, wage insurance, and help for small firms—so cleaner growth strengthens local jobs rather than displacing them.
